T*
(## 5. User Roles) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Role | What the role does |) Tj
T*
(| --- | --- |) Tj
T*
(| Citizen | Registers, submits complaints, views public board, tracks own complaints, gives) Tj
T*
(feedback, and raises objections. |) Tj
T*
(| Central Officer | Accepts/rejects submitted complaints, routes accepted complaints to wards,) Tj
T*
(manages officers/teams/wards/drains, and views reports and high-risk zones. |) Tj
T*
(| Ward Officer | Verifies ward complaints, rejects or marks duplicate complaints, assigns or) Tj
T*
(changes maintenance teams, handles support requests, reviews objections, and manages) Tj
T*
(disputed/reopened cases. |) Tj
T*
(| Maintenance Team / Maintenance Member | Receives assigned work, starts work, requests support,) Tj
T*
(uploads completion proof, and views task history/feedback. |) Tj
T*
(| Inspector | Reviews solved-by-team cases, checks proof, approves work, marks false completion,) Tj
T*
(and records inspection decisions. |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 6. Full Workflow Explanation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Citizen) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Citizen submits a complaint from `pages/citizen/submit-complaint.php`.) Tj
T*
(- `auth/submit_complaint_process.php` inserts the complaint into `complaints` with status) Tj
T*
(`submitted`.) Tj
T*
(- Uploaded complaint images/videos are stored in `assets/uploads/complaints/` and recorded in) Tj
T*
(`complaint_media`.) Tj
T*
(- A status record is inserted in `complaint_status_logs`.) Tj
T*
(- Central officers receive rows in `central_notifications`.) Tj
T*
(- Citizen-facing visibility is provided through `pages/citizen/public-board.php`,) Tj
T*
(`pages/citizen/my-complaints.php`, and `pages/citizen/track-complaint.php`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Central Officer) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Submitted complaints appear in `pages/central/complaints.php`.) Tj
T*
(- The Central Officer accepts or rejects a complaint.) Tj
T*
(- Accepted complaints move to `received`.) Tj
T*
(- Rejected complaints are recorded in `complaint_decisions` and move to `rejected_by_central`.) Tj
T*
(- Accepted complaints go to `pages/central/routing-assignment.php`.) Tj
T*
(- Routing inserts `complaint_assignments` with `assignment_status = 'ward_assigned'` and changes) Tj
T*
(complaint status to `pending_verification`.) Tj
T*
(- Citizens and ward officers receive notification rows.) Tj
T*
(- Accepted/rejected records remain visible in `pages/central/processed-complaints.php`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Ward Officer) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Routed complaints appear in `pages/ward/verification-queue.php`.) Tj
T*
(- Ward Officer can verify, reject, or mark duplicate.) Tj
T*
(- Verified complaints move to `verified_by_ward`.) Tj
T*
(- Verified complaints move to `pages/ward/local-team-assignment.php` for local team assignment.) Tj
T*
(- Assignment updates `complaint_assignments.maintenance_team_id`, `assignment_status`,) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
