T*
(`pages/ward/false-completion-reviews.php`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Maintenance Team) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Assigned work appears in `pages/maintenance/assigned-tasks.php`.) Tj
T*
(- The team starts work; complaint and assignment can move to `in_progress`.) Tj
T*
(- Active work appears in `pages/maintenance/in-progress-work.php`.) Tj
T*
(- Support can be requested through `notifications/send_maintenance_support_request.php`, which) Tj
T*
(inserts `maintenance_support_requests` and notifies the Ward Officer.) Tj
T*
(- Completion proof is uploaded from `pages/maintenance/upload-completion-proof.php`.) Tj
T*
(- Proof files are stored in `assets/uploads/maintenance_proofs/` and metadata is inserted into) Tj
T*
(`maintenance_proofs`.) Tj
T*
(- The assignment is marked `completed`, the complaint moves toward `solved_by_team` / inspector) Tj
T*
(review, and inspectors receive notification.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Inspector) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Solved cases appear in `pages/inspector/solved-cases.php` and inspection pages.) Tj
T*
(- Inspector reviews before/after details in `pages/inspector/before-after-review.php` and) Tj
T*
(decisions in `pages/inspector/inspection-queue.php`.) Tj
T*
(- Approval inserts `inspection_logs`, changes the complaint to `closed`, accepts proof, and) Tj
T*
(notifies related roles.) Tj
T*
(- False completion inserts `inspection_logs`, changes the complaint to `disputed`, and sends it) Tj
T*
(back for ward dispute handling.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Feedback / Objection / Dispute) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Citizen feedback and objections are submitted from `pages/citizen/feedback-reopen.php`.) Tj
T*
(- Normal feedback inserts into `feedbacks` with `feedback_type = 'feedback'` and may create) Tj
T*
(`maintenance_team_reviews`.) Tj
T*
(- Bad feedback/objection inserts `feedbacks` with `feedback_type = 'false_completion'`, inserts) Tj
T*
(`reopen_requests`, and changes the complaint to `disputed`.) Tj
T*
(- Ward, central, inspector, and maintenance notification rows are created where recipient data) Tj
T*
(exists.) Tj
T*
(- Valid objection/dispute can reopen or reassign a complaint; invalid objection can be) Tj
T*
(rejected/resolved.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(A main strength of the project is real-time complaint tracking through status changes and the) Tj
T*
(role-wise notification system.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 7. Core Features) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Feature | Actual evidence in project |) Tj
T*
(| --- | --- |) Tj
T*
(| Login and role-based redirection | `auth/login.php`, `auth/login_process.php`,) Tj
T*
ET
