(- `login_access` in `users`, allowing login to be enabled/disabled without deleting users.) Tj
T*
(- `user_status` in `users`, supporting `active`, `inactive`, `suspended`, and `banned`.) Tj
T*
(- Role-based page access using session role checks and `$allowed_role` / `$allowed_roles`.) Tj
T*
(- Prepared statements for dynamic SQL queries.) Tj
T*
(- Forgot password/reset token support through `auth/forgot_password.php`,) Tj
T*
(`auth/reset_password.php`, `users.reset_token`, and `users.reset_time`.) Tj
T*
(- Remember-me token support through `remember_tokens` with hashed validators.) Tj
T*
